metadata.description: Katy Keene, model/actress/singer extraordinaire, has been an inspiration for the fashion-conscious for years! But, the queen of chic has her hands full with the Hollywood lifestyle. Can she keep the balancing act together and keep her fans wowed? Prepare to experience the glitz and glamour in stories like "Oh Doctor Killdear", "Help Wanted Female" and more!
metadata.name: Katy Keene
